metadata.name: DEVIL MONKEY 'DMK' - gas mask
metadata.description:
[Graffiti artist devil monkey 'DMK' (original version)]

'dmk' is a graffiti artist & extreme sports monkey with passion and energy.

 This work is the 2nd theme 'gas mask'. It is an important preparation for a graffiti. 

It marks the beginning of his passionate creative activities. and He has superpowers.

His graffiti comes to life like magic. dmk makes friends with graffiti. His body burns with passion and energy. 

He is not afraid of challenges and has strong self-confidence. He has a good personality and helps his friends in trouble. 

His passion is like fire and his energy is in his eyes. When you are tired and tired, dmk emotionally presents you with passion and energy. 

'dmk' is always your passionate friend.
